1- Download arduino IDE.
2- Open arduino, File>> preferences>> insert the link "https://dl.espressif.com/dl/package_esp32_index.json" , then Ok.
3- Tools>> board:"arduino">> board manager>> select ESP32 and install.
4- Tools>> board>> ESP32 arduino>> select ESP32 Dev module.
5- Oonnect the electronic piece to the computer using USB port.
6- Tools>> prot>> choose COM26.
7- To test the electronic piece: File>> Example>> 0.1 basics>> Blink>> and run.
